              </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
              <span class="iconz fa-stack fa-4x" ng-class="{fadeIn: favcons.flags.down, iconz: favcons.flags.up}">
                  <img src="http://www.sproutsanfrancisco.com/shop/media/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/150x150/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/e/nesting_dolls.jpg">
