              </p>
          </div>
      </div>
      </div> <!-- zum-waypoints -->
    </div>
  </section>
<div ng-show="barready" class="ng-hide">
  <section class="success" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h1>Relevant Hashtags</h1>
          <hr class="star-light">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg">
          <p>According our calculations, here are the most relevant hashtags to what you just searched. It works on the law of averages, so the more times people search that hashtag, the more accurate it will become!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 text-left">
          <canvas barchart options="myChartOptions" data="myData" width="700" height="400"></canvas>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
